### Complete Lean 4 Proof

```lean4
theorem nullmeasurable_measurable_null {s : Set ℝ} (h : NullMeasurableSet s volume) :
    ∃ t ⊆ s, MeasurableSet t ∧ volume t = volume s ∧ volume (s \ t) = 0 := by
  have h_main : ∃ t ⊆ s, MeasurableSet t ∧ volume t = volume s ∧ volume (s \ t) = 0 := by
